data.description: Opportunity Knocks! ! Spacious End Unit Townhome in Desirable Cherry Tree Village! Open floor plan features foyer, living room w/ gas fireplace, formal dining room, sun drenched eat in kitchen w/ wood floor & stainless steel appliances, 3 generous sized bedrooms with abundant closet space, 2 1/2 updated baths, laundry area plus finished basement w/ family room and access to fenced in stamped concrete patio. The development offers tennis courts, basketball court and a playground! Conveniently located near parkway, train station and the ferry! Great location, minutes to everything!
